    <date day="27" month="March" year="2023"/>
    <abstract>
      <t>Sieve Email Filtering Language (RFC 5228) is a popular email
   filtering language used upon final mail delivery.  This document
   creates a registry of Sieve (RFC 5228) actions in order to help
   developers and Sieve extension writers track interactions between
   different extensions.</t>
    </abstract>
  </front>
